{
  "stem": "19807.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They begin to-- we begin to get-- we began to hear the trains are being assembled.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'm talking now from a perspective of the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you've seen the books that you read, you see that there was a delegation that went to the king.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they formed from the intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The clergy with-- God save their soul-- Metropolit Stephan and Metropolit Kirill went to the king on our behalf.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't know any of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "All I knew I'm hearing all from my parents, we're doomed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We're ready to be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the night came that we're-- we're really assembled by the police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they came and took us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they put us together in the school yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we're waiting to be shipped out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother at that time said, it is not going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's the time after that we found out that the clergy went and pleaded for our lives in our behalf.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I had promised my mother [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sorry-- the day would come after it was all over that I will go back and pray at the graves of these two-- these great clergymen, these bishops that really put themselves on the line, which is unheard of anywhere in the world.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I just went back there and I paid all my respects.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But those days, as we were assembled, I did not know that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in my meeting with the bishop, the very recent meeting, he told us that the bishop came to the churchyard, got up on a bench, and at the top of his voice said, children, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You will be saved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
